data.name: label1.Text
data.value:
This tool fixes the "driver is not supported" error on HP Softpaq driver packages. Copyright © 2022 Josh Davidson
Instructions:
- Run all driver setup programs even if they will display the not supported message
- All packages need to be extracted to the same folder (ex: C:\SWsetup)
- Return to this wizard and select the extracted folder (usually C:\SWsetup)
- Click Next to search for patchable driver setup programs
